_sText:
Ok, this is my fourth map and for sure my best of the four! It took less than a day to make because it is small but even with bots its really great fun! It is loaded with features including:

-Two sniper towers
-Underground tunnel system
-Custom lighting
-Slits in the walls of the spawn rooms
-A big garden in the middle
-Scouts and a shotgun can be found in the map
-Buy zones
-20 spawns for each team
-Cs_militia skybox
-Nav file


IMPORTANT: It will most likely give you a message when you play this map saying that the nav file was created on a different version of the map! This is fine, it is because I created the nav file on my second to last test of the map. On my last edit, I just moved a tree and added some more lights, so the bots should move fine. But, if it gets annoying just type nav_analyze in console and wait...
